title: Ainsley's Taste of Malta
overview: Ainsley Harriott is hitting the road again, this time his travels take him to beautiful Malta. A cultural mash up of Sicilian, British, Spanish and even French culture, the cuisine and tradition in Malta offers a rich territory for Ainsley to explore! Rich culinary traditions see rabbit stews served beside mellow goat's cheese, irresistible soft bread and honeyed desserts, in a fusion of Mediterranean and Arabic influence.
